        <td width="69%" valign="top" align="center"><br>
<table border="1" width="469" cellspacing="0" align="center">
  <tr>
	<td width="463" valign="top" class="TD2"><b><u><font size="2" color="#CC0000">Credit Card Processing Integration</font></u><br><br>
    Credit card processing is an easy and secured way to charge your customer's credit card. Payments go directly to the bank account you setup with your Merchant 
    provider.<br><br><font color="#CC0000" size="2"><u>How does it work?</font></u><br><br>First, check with your Merchant provider if you can process credit cards 
    through the following integrated credit card processing Gateways: Authorize.net and/or Fidelity Payment Systems.<br>
    Second, setup the Merchant Services page with the required credentials: API Log and Transaction Key.<br><br>
    <u><font size="2" color="#CC0000">How to start?</font></u><br><br>First, you need to setup a Merchant account. Contact the above credit card 
    processing Gateways. These are the ones integrated in the Moving Software.</b></td>
  </tr>
</table>
  <br>
